## Component Auto-Import

Nuxt 3 automatically imports:
- All `Ol*` components from `@paradoxai/ui`
- All `El*` components from Element Plus
- Vue 3 Composition API functions
- Nuxt composables

No explicit imports needed:
```vue
<script setup lang="ts">
// ref, computed, watch, etc. are auto-imported
const count = ref(0)
const doubled = computed(() => count.value * 2)
</script>

<template>
  <!-- OlButton, OlDialog, etc. are auto-imported -->
  <OlButton @click="count++">Click</OlButton>
</template>
```

